br /><br />It is making me want to go back and read her well-loved book, <a href="https://goodreads.com/book/show/28789711.SPQR_A_History_of_Ancient_Rome" title="SPQR A History of Ancient Rome by Mary Beard" rel="noopener">SPQR: A History of Ancient Rome</a>, because if anyone can bring it to life, surely it is Mary Beard.<br /><br /><i>The publisher provided a copy of this book through Edelweiss in exchange for an honest review. </i></span></div></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"><ul class="CollapsableList"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/68030?shelf=ebooks" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">ebooks</span></a> <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/68030?shelf=essays" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">essays</span></a> <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/68030?shelf=read2017" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">read2017</span></a> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small" aria-label="Show all items in the list"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></ul></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">83 likes</span></button></div><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">7 comments</span></button></div></div><div data-testid="actions"><div class="SocialFooter__action"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem"><i class="Icon LikeIcon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.4813282,6.41129383 L14.586127,6.97676